      "text": "We are considering re-using urlbar modules in products other than Firefox desktop, as well as for Firefox desktop's search bar (if Firefox desktop is to offer a separate search bar in the future). To that end, this bug tracks work that needs to be done for the urlbar modules to be shared. For details see: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1g37DHbs1fTHex2Q0_zbnHF9FhlaVw6mMeOMKXxqIdaY/edit?pli=1",
